original: Jeansson, Allan Johan Edvard, direktör, Kalmar, f. 10/5/92 i Ljungby av dir. Ernst J. o. Anna Pettersson. G. 15 m. Erica Pohle. Barn: Björn f. 16, tegelmäst.. Smedby, Sigfrid 18, kamr., Kalmar, Haide 21, g. m. avd:-chef Axed J :son Bergström, Sthlm, Roland 22, kassör, Kalmar. — Realex., CTI, stud. i Tyskl. 10-11. Kont. h. Kalmar L. Lantmän 11, kassör i Ny-gärde Tegelbr. A-B 12, disp. 15 o. dir. sed. 31, disp. i A-B Berga Tegelbr. fr. 25 o. dir. sed. 31. Led. av styr. f. Rederi A-B Kalmare Nyckel o. A-B Kalmar Tennishall, ordf. i Kalmar pistolkil., tled. av styr. f. Sv. pistoliskytte-förb.
translated: Jeansson, Allan Johan Edvard, director, Kalmar, b. 10/5/92 in Ljungby to director Ernst J. and Anna Pettersson. M. 15 with Erica Pohle. Children: Björn b. 16, bricklayer. Smedby, Sigfrid b. 18, clerk, Kalmar, Haide b. 21, m. to department head Axed J:son Bergström, Stockholm, Roland b. 22, treasurer, Kalmar. - Secondary school, CTI, studied in Germany 10-11. Worked at Kalmar L. Lantmän 11, treasurer at Ny-gärde Brickworks A-B 12, manager 15 and director since 31, manager at Berga Brickworks A-B from 25 and director since 31. Member of the board of Rederi A-B Kalmare Nyckel and A-B Kalmar Tennis Hall, chairman of Kalmar Pistol Club, deputy member of the board of the Swedish Pistol Shooting Association.
